title: Kerry, Netanyahu to discuss Israeli-Palestinian tensions
text:
> Top News Kerry, Netanyahu to discuss Israeli-Palestinian tensions Secretary of State John Kerry talks about foreign policy priorities during a speech at Indiana University in Bloomington, Ind., Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015. Kerry spoke to mark the opening of the new building for IU's School of Global and International Studies. (AP Photo/Michael Conroy) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team!
